{"type":null,"faqId":9774,"title":"荣耀畅玩版（g750-t01）如何添加/取消闹钟","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击<b>时钟</b>。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>进入闹钟界面。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30275\" /></span><span><span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，进入设置闹钟界面，可以进行如下操作：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>滑动闹钟下方的时间框，设置闹钟铃响的时间。如下：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img style=\"width:190px;height:79px;\" height=\"216\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30278\" width=\"190\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击<b>重复</b>，选择需要闹钟重复的周期，如下：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img style=\"width:270px;height:93px;\" height=\"130\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30277\" width=\"270\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击<b>铃声</b>，选择闹钟铃声。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>滑动音量，调节闹钟音量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>勾选<b>振动</b>，设置手机在闹钟铃响时振动。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击<b>标签，</b>输入闹钟时间名称。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击<b>完成</b>，完成闹钟的添加。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>在闹钟界面，可以看到当前所有闹钟的列表，去掉一条闹钟后面的勾选，就表示取消了这个闹钟。或长按一条闹钟记录，在弹出菜单中选择“<b>删除闹钟</b>”删除您选择的闹钟。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"390","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396318018000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":197,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"闹钟","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}